    "The background export task was terminated by iOS before completing." : {
      "comment" : "Detailed error: task expired"
    },
    "The metrics injected into your daily note match exactly what you've enabled in Export Settings → Health Metrics. Change your metric selection there to control what gets injected." : {

    },
    "This folder will be created inside your selected export location. Leave empty to export directly to the root folder." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dieser Ordner wird innerhalb des ausgewählten Exportziels erstellt. Leer lassen, um direkt in den Stammordner zu exportieren."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This folder will be created inside your selected export location. Leave empty to export directly to the root folder."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esta carpeta se creará dentro de tu ubicación de exportación seleccionada. Deja vacío para exportar directamente a la carpeta raíz."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ce dossier sera créé dans votre emplacement d'exportation sélectionné. Laissez vide pour exporter directement dans le dossier racine."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Questa cartella verrà creata nella posizione di esportazione selezionata. Lascia vuoto per esportare direttamente nella cartella principale."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "このフォルダは選択したエクスポート先に作成されます。ルートフォルダに直接エクスポートする場合は空のままにしてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 폴더는 선택한 내보내기 위치 안에 생성됩니다. 루트 폴더로 직접 내보내려면 비워 두세요."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Deze map wordt aangemaakt in je geselecteerde exportlocatie. Laat leeg om rechtstreeks naar de hoofdmap te exporteren."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esta pasta será criada dentro do local de exportação selecionado. Deixe vazio para exportar diretamente na pasta raiz."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此文件夹将在您选择的导出位置内创建。留空则直接导出到根文件夹。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This iPad is discoverable by Health.md on Mac" : {

    },
    "This will remove all health data cached on this Mac. You can re-sync from your iPhone at any time." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hiermit werden alle auf diesem Mac zwischengespeicherten Gesundheitsdaten entfernt. Sie können jederzeit erneut von Ihrem iPhone synchronisieren."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This will remove all health data cached on this Mac. You can re-sync from your iPhone at any time."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esto eliminará todos los datos de salud almacenados en caché en este Mac. Puedes volver a sincronizar desde tu iPhone en cualquier momento."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cela supprimera toutes les données de santé mises en cache sur ce Mac. Vous pouvez resynchroniser depuis votre iPhone à tout moment."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Questo rimuoverà tutti i dati sanitari memorizzati su questo Mac. Puoi sincronizzare nuovamente dal tuo iPhone in qualsiasi momento."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "このMacにキャッシュされたすべてのヘルスデータが削除されます。iPhoneからいつでも再同期できます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 Mac에 캐시된 모든 건강 데이터가 삭제됩니다. 언제든지 iPhone에서 다시 동기화할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dit verwijdert alle gezondheidsgegevens die op deze Mac zijn opgeslagen. Je kunt op elk moment opnieuw synchroniseren vanaf je iPhone."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Isso removerá todos os dados de saúde armazenados em cache neste Mac. Você pode sincronizar novamente pelo seu iPhone a qualquer momento."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这将删除缓存在此 Mac 上的所有健康数据。您可以随时从 iPhone 重新同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will sync your entire health data history from your iPhone. Depending on how much data you have, this could take several minutes.\n\nMake sure Health.md stays open on your iPhone during the sync." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hiermit wird Ihr gesamter Gesundheitsdatenverlauf von Ihrem iPhone synchronisiert. Je nach Datenmenge kann dies einige Minuten dauern.\n\nStellen Sie sicher, dass Health.md während der Synchronisierung auf Ihrem iPhone geöffnet bleibt."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This will sync your entire health data history from your iPhone. Depending on how much data you have, this could take several minutes.\n\nMake sure Health.md stays open on your iPhone during the sync."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esto sincronizará todo tu historial de datos de salud desde tu iPhone. Dependiendo de la cantidad de datos que tengas, esto podría tardar varios minutos.\n\nAsegúrate de que Health.md permanezca abierto en tu iPhone durante la sincronización."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cela synchronisera l'intégralité de votre historique de données de santé depuis votre iPhone. Selon la quantité de données, cela peut prendre plusieurs minutes.\n\nAssurez-vous que Health.md reste ouvert sur votre iPhone pendant la synchronisation."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Questa operazione sincronizzerà l'intera cronologia dei dati sanitari dal tuo iPhone. A seconda della quantità di dati, potrebbe richiedere diversi minuti.\n\nAssicurati che Health.md rimanga aperto sul tuo iPhone durante la sincronizzazione."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "iPhoneからすべてのヘルスデータ履歴を同期します。データ量によっては数分かかる場合があります。\n\n同期中はiPhoneでHealth.mdを開いたままにしてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "iPhone에서 전체 건강 데이터 기록을 동기화합니다. 데이터 양에 따라 몇 분 정도 걸릴 수 있습니다.\n\n동기화 중에 iPhone에서 Health.md가 열려 있는지 확인하세요."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dit synchroniseert je volledige gezondheidsgeschiedenis vanaf je iPhone. Afhankelijk van de hoeveelheid gegevens kan dit enkele minuten duren.\n\nZorg dat Health.md geopend blijft op je iPhone tijdens het synchroniseren."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Isso sincronizará todo o seu histórico de dados de saúde do seu iPhone. Dependendo da quantidade de dados, isso pode levar vários minutos.\n\nCertifique-se de que o Health.md permaneça aberto no seu iPhone durante a sincronização."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这将从您的 iPhone 同步全部健康数据历史记录。根据数据量大小，这可能需要几分钟时间。\n\n请确保同步期间 Health.md 在 iPhone 上保持打开状态。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
